body.body: Triumph Diagnostic Tool 2022-08 Update - Calibrations Removed From Service

Following a further review of Instrument and Chassis ECM calibration downloads contained in the Triumph Diagnostic Tool, we have identified that a number of market specific calibrations are no longer required. The affected calibrations will be removed from the diagnostic tool from the
The instrument calibrations that will be removed are detailed below, along with details of the calibrations which should now be used instead.

The Chassis ECM calibrations that will be removed are detailed below, along with details of the "All markets unless a market specific calibration exists" calibrations which should now be used instead.
